            article
                .content.col-xs-12.col-sm-7.col-md-8.col-lg-9
                    h3 Job Description
                    p We're seeking an Assistant Account Executive to join our team! This entry level opportunity will allow you to begin to learn from some of the brightest, smartest and most creative people in the industry. You'll be helping to drive and carry out the execution of projects - flawlessly - across this client's business. We'd like to see someone who can be a buttoned down business leader and think and act proactively. You'll help keep structure and manage internal relationships. And your strategic viewpoint and solid ideas will be welcome.
                    h3 Desired Skills and Experience
                    p You'll have had an internship or entry level experience in a marketing related field, as well as experiences that have fostered leadership experience. A passion for creativity is a must. A bachelor's degree in marketing is needed. You're an active listener, you're solution focused and results driven and you know that it's all about details, details, details. Be curious. Be proactive.  We look forward to meeting you!
